e_{ss}&=\lim_{s \to 0} s\Phi_e(s)\frac{A}{s^2}=\lim_{s \to 0}\frac{A\left[sT + 1 - \frac{K}{s}G_c(s)\right]}{s(Ts + 1) + K}=\frac{A\left[1 - \frac{K}{s}G_c(s)\right]}{K}=0
